[[Image tiddlers|Images and Attachments]] can be simply displayed within other tiddlers via [[transclusion|Transclusions]]:

{{Sn:WikitextImageTransclusion||MagicSnippet}}

Using the `img` link-like syntax, you can also specify a size:

{{Sn:WikitextImageImgify||MagicSnippet}}

The `img` syntax can also directly include images available at a web URL:

{{Sn:WikitextWebImage||MagicSnippet}}

For more on including images in your wiki, see [[Images and Attachments]].
